{"tid":131310,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"飛行意大利麵條神，連登正式招信徒","createTime":"2017-02-23T03:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T12:13:05.000Z","uid":59014,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f320c7f95dfeca8c9a1590e8a3a6281961d73cb","tid":131310,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74baa1de8fb477814584fe8ea8f006fcd87903a","tid":131310,"uid":9681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:54:31.000Z","msg":"你有冇笠筲箕喺頭上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48821eb2920462734efe01519b8bcfe67dd343c8","tid":131310,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:56:58.000Z","msg":"憑着數千虔誠的崇拜者，甚至數百萬，飛天麵條神教被廣泛認為是一個合法的宗教。即使是它的反對者－主要是基督教的原教旨主義者，也承認我們上帝的球(指兩顆肉丸)比他們的大。"},{"pid":"8a5bbdb52b1a2f60f9e942e90a5e60850a332f13","tid":131310,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:57:44.000Z","msg":"根據《飛行麵條怪的福音》，本教正式的祈禱結束語是「RAmen」（音：拉門寬式IPA：/ˈlaːmɛn/）。該詞是一個混成詞，由一個閃族詞「阿門」（Amen）（猶太教、基督教和伊斯蘭教均將此詞作為祈禱用語）和「拉麵」（Ramen）混合而來。另一種解釋是，因為意大利麵條源自中國（實際上是美國人的誤解），所以「RAmen」其實是麵條怪更道地的稱呼方式。該詞在拼寫時一般大寫「R」和「A」，但只大寫首字母「R」也可以接受"},{"pid":"8388acc474d429fb90d0dc2b2d0bc7bea3668e3b","tid":131310,"uid":6537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:58:11.000Z","msg":"me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d493f524067cb480e8f7300cf6125bb65e4a3117","tid":131310,"uid":34791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:59:07.000Z","msg":"信左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be3e57feaa538271c980ce3fc59303d6c2b5278","tid":131310,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:02:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=AWC6xsxbiAY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAWC6xsxbiAY&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtULxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=6520f8c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=AWC6xsxbiAY</a><br />\n<br />\n請相信祂<br />\n<br />\n祂是我們的主，世界如此不公平，有瑕疵<br />\n<br />\n是因為麵神當時喝醉後造世界，造人"},{"pid":"41fccc3f4bcc0c44a4bcd205e88121cc8a86e5d1","tid":131310,"uid":39470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:08:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79448a6de9084389b4eadf08b3b271314fa52dc8","tid":131310,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:24:45.000Z","msg":"問過小丑神未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢咪等於高/連/膠登嘅FSM囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a93e9ea12fbcef38619ea349c765531940340ac","tid":131310,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:09:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問過小丑神未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢咪等於高/連/膠登嘅FSM囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n麵神係某國家係合法，信徒都過千萬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小丑神什麼都不是"},{"pid":"0da88c7b0f27e077fd6e5c4a39ce4e84cb02f196","tid":131310,"uid":30830,"like":0